<ol>
<li><p>Online Deposit</p>
<ul>
<li><p>Step 1: Select the Payment Method you wish to use;</p>
</li>
<li><p>Step 2: Enter the amount you wish to deposit into your account in the given text fields;</p>
</li>
<li><p>Step 3: Click on the &quot;Top Up Now&quot; button;</p>
</li>
<li><p>Step 4: You will be prompted to follow instructions on your mobile phone to complete the transaction. If this is successful, the money will be credited to your account.</p>
